{"tid":461842,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 一齊玩揭尾故！15","createTime":"2017-11-08T04:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T11:06:40.000Z","uid":136763,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7f515ec78ac5c80ab1a17a7389fbf0221df1084f","tid":461842,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的 馬田 陳仔 同另外三人<br />\n大隻佬 爛口強 mk妹 <br />\n參加poly旅會嘅旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飛機失事！墜落雪山 <br />\n全機得返佢地五個<br />\n除咗馬田隻錶 其他器材都跌爛<br />\n陳仔隻腳嚴重受傷<br />\n行都行唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飢寒交迫之下 <br />\n佢地搵到一間已荒廢嘅正方木屋<br />\n渡過咗一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 得馬田被救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底發生咗咩事！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n改編自另一個故 <br />\n聽過嘅巴打好易估到<br />\n所以 聽過嘅巴打忍忍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未聽過嘅 10頁內定能爆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝各位連日嚟嘅支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意小弟嘅創作請留個正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題問時請將範圍縮小 並以是非題題問 <br />\n<br />\n劣質創作 敬請見諒"},{"pid":"f60ead65f8261d620811c35e11219a1d470b25ab","tid":461842,"uid":69429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"隻錶重要？<br />\n馬田有錶所以得救？<br />\n其他人全部死？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 係咪世界奇妙物語定奇幻潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7aaffb9bbb35666231fd5152c113cbd7eaab64","tid":46